title: Daily Wire Backstage: No, It Doesn’t Take A Village
description:
Can Elon Musk actually save the time-sucking hellscape known as Twitter? Has poor Walt Disney’s frozen body turned full slushy from spinning in its grave after the company’s “not-at-all-secret gay agenda” was exposed? … And, now that the world’s best selling cookie has gone woke, are the rumors true that Jeremy is busy making a better Oreo? Hmm…   

Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, Matt Walsh, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing to find out. Plus Tim Pool crashes the Daily Wire studios!
